### Sin action explícito (se infiere de la instrucción)
POST {{llmBase}}/document-action
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "document_ids": [10],
  "instruction": "Haceme una lista de todas las obligaciones y responsabilidades mencionadas en este documento",
  "chat_id": {{chatId}}
}


### compare (dos documentos)
POST {{llmBase}}/document-action
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "document_ids": [10, 11],
  "instruction": "Compará estos dos documentos e identificá similitudes y diferencias",
  "action": "compare",
  "chat_id": {{chatId}}
}


### report
POST {{llmBase}}/document-action
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "document_ids": [10],
  "instruction": "Generá un reporte formal sobre el contenido de este documento",
  "action": "report",
  "chat_id": {{chatId}}
}


### analyze
POST {{llmBase}}/document-action
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "document_ids": [10],
  "instruction": "Hacé un análisis detallado de este documento",
